name: Food or Not!
description:
Put the food on a skewer! Play fast and smart!
Easy to play. Just catch edible items and miss inedibles!
Show your skills in different locations - you can become a fruit master in the jungle or sushi master in Japan!

Highlights:
*Simple and easy swipe to enjoy fun of realistic catching delicious food!
*Unlock different locations such as city, Japan, jungle, Mars or winter!
*Enjoy pleasant music for each location
*A lot of various tasty items such as donuts, fruits, sushi and many others!
